WEBVTT

00:55.389 --> 00:59.058
We spoke of those times,
painful and lamented,

00:59.184 --> 01:03.354
when passion is the joy
and martyrdom of youth.

01:18.704 --> 01:22.248
An Eye for Beauty

02:08.587 --> 02:10.546
ln the centuries that follow,

02:11.173 --> 02:15.760
a civilization is always judged
by its architecture.

02:16.804 --> 02:19.806
Building is an activity of hope.

02:19.932 --> 02:22.683
The hope that what we create will be useful

02:22.810 --> 02:23.768
and beautiful.

02:24.686 --> 02:28.231
The hope of telling future generations
who we were.

02:29.066 --> 02:31.359
And the hope they will be moved,

02:31.485 --> 02:35.780
as we were by the architecture
of those who came before us.

02:37.324 --> 02:38.324
Thank you.

02:45.499 --> 02:47.583
We love your work.
- Bravo!

02:47.709 --> 02:49.252
Thank you so much.

02:49.378 --> 02:52.797
Canada is magnificent.
The prairies, mountains...

02:52.923 --> 02:53.965
The wild animals.

02:54.091 --> 02:56.050
Forgive me, l have to go.

02:56.176 --> 02:57.468
Again, bravo!
- Thank you.

02:58.971 --> 03:00.304
Where are we tomorrow?

03:00.430 --> 03:02.390
The Booksellers Award.

03:05.060 --> 03:07.270
Congratulations, Mr Sauvageau.

03:08.689 --> 03:09.730
Thanks.

03:09.857 --> 03:10.815
Thanks a lot.

05:10.435 --> 05:11.936
Here's our man!

05:13.355 --> 05:14.480
Hello, darling.

05:14.606 --> 05:15.272
You OK?

05:15.983 --> 05:17.024
Hey there!

05:18.610 --> 05:20.111
We started.
- Perfect.

05:21.989 --> 05:22.989
You made it!

05:23.865 --> 05:25.950
Things good?
- Fine, you?

05:26.827 --> 05:28.369
Hey bud.
- Dude.

05:29.413 --> 05:30.538
How was Toronto?

05:30.664 --> 05:31.622
Uneventful.

05:32.582 --> 05:34.083
Don't you avoid juries?

05:34.209 --> 05:35.543
On principle, yes.

05:35.669 --> 05:39.213
But they pay $1 500 per day plus expenses.

05:40.048 --> 05:42.800
These days l can't afford principles.

05:43.176 --> 05:45.302
Sure, and you drive a T-Bird.

05:46.471 --> 05:49.557
Bought at auction. Cheaper than a Toyota.

05:49.683 --> 05:51.892
But a way classier image.

05:52.019 --> 05:54.103
Aren't you building a house?

05:55.355 --> 05:56.897
One. For a lawyer.

05:57.024 --> 05:59.316
Hard to squeeze money from a lawyer.

06:00.527 --> 06:02.611
Who else was on the jury?

06:03.613 --> 06:05.656
Canada in all its splendor.

06:06.575 --> 06:08.242
A guy from the West Coast,

06:08.744 --> 06:10.536
who'd worked with Arthur Erickson.

06:11.038 --> 06:12.163
RlP.

06:13.206 --> 06:14.582
One from Saskatoon,

06:14.708 --> 06:15.666
half-Native,

06:15.792 --> 06:17.835
so politically desirable.

06:18.420 --> 06:20.129
A big designer from Toronto...

06:20.589 --> 06:21.589
lnevitably.

06:21.715 --> 06:23.799
And an engineer from Halifax.

06:23.925 --> 06:25.718
Semi-incompetent, but

06:25.844 --> 06:29.597
he lives a stone's throw from the Atlantic.

06:29.723 --> 06:30.639
From sea to sea.

06:31.224 --> 06:35.102
And the chairwoman. Faculty dean, decorated,

06:35.228 --> 06:36.771
and Jewish. lrreproachable.

06:36.897 --> 06:39.315
And the token French-Canadian.

06:39.441 --> 06:40.066
Yours truly!

07:57.060 --> 07:58.435
How's your plantation?

07:59.813 --> 08:01.147
Come see.
- Now?

08:01.273 --> 08:02.690
Sure.

08:06.987 --> 08:07.945
Not coming?

08:09.739 --> 08:10.656
For the walk.

08:11.449 --> 08:14.285
l did two hours of track today.
l'll stay put.

08:18.540 --> 08:19.248
Here.

08:20.458 --> 08:21.292
ls this it?

08:25.714 --> 08:28.507
Seeds from Humboldt County.
- California?

08:32.929 --> 08:34.346
Sinsemilla?

08:35.015 --> 08:35.931
Even better.

08:36.266 --> 08:37.141
A new hybrid.

10:24.165 --> 10:25.416
What's this?

10:25.875 --> 10:28.294
A steel angle. One on each side.

10:28.420 --> 10:29.628
lt's not strong enough.

10:29.963 --> 10:32.006
