10:32.132 --> 10:33.674
lt can't budge.

10:33.800 --> 10:35.259
So what do you want?

10:40.974 --> 10:42.975
Bad back?
- lt's been a month.

10:43.643 --> 10:45.477
Walking hurts like hell.

10:46.062 --> 10:47.646
Go see lsabelle.
- No time!

10:48.648 --> 10:51.817
l need something like this.

10:51.943 --> 10:52.651
ln steel.

10:55.655 --> 10:58.198
How will you hide it?

10:58.325 --> 10:59.241
Furring.

10:59.617 --> 11:00.993
No, not furring.

11:01.119 --> 11:02.661
lt'll be hideous.

11:02.787 --> 11:05.289
You're the architect. Find a solution.

11:05.999 --> 11:07.708
l'll find something.

11:30.440 --> 11:33.901
When the Montreal symphony hall opened

11:34.027 --> 11:37.112
the architect was barely mentioned.

11:37.238 --> 11:41.408
The politicians crowed
while critics blasted the acoustician.

11:41.534 --> 11:43.452
Palais Montcalm, same thing.

11:43.578 --> 11:46.914
When our firm designed the Laval hospital,

11:47.040 --> 11:49.792
we weren't invited to the inauguration!

11:49.918 --> 11:52.211
The mayor, ministers, execs...

11:52.337 --> 11:54.588
even the Mafia was invited.

11:54.714 --> 11:56.215
But not the architects!

11:56.341 --> 11:57.299
An oversight.

11:58.093 --> 12:00.511
