12:00.637 --> 12:03.430
An architect's only as good as his client.

12:03.556 --> 12:06.642
At least you can teach. You love it.

12:06.768 --> 12:08.018
l just can't.

12:08.978 --> 12:10.145
That's life.

12:10.271 --> 12:11.355
She's an MD, l'm an RN.

12:11.481 --> 12:13.440
