30:36.335 --> 30:37.335
Good trip?

30:37.461 --> 30:38.169
Excellent.

30:42.424 --> 30:43.382
You OK?

30:43.509 --> 30:44.217
Fine.

30:44.551 --> 30:45.551
Nothing special?

30:46.053 --> 30:46.969
Nope.

30:47.471 --> 30:48.346
You?

30:48.972 --> 30:50.515
