35:57.030 --> 35:59.323
Luc Sauvageau has talent.

36:02.369 --> 36:03.452
Luc,

36:04.371 --> 36:09.750
Gigi and l will live in the most
beautiful house on the North Shore.

36:09.876 --> 36:10.501
Thank you.

36:10.919 --> 36:11.961
Thank you so much!

36:12.712 --> 36:13.879
Very kind. Look...

36:14.422 --> 36:15.548
May l?

36:17.425 --> 36:20.761
l designed it, but Roger built it.

36:21.638 --> 36:22.346
Cheers.

36:28.186 --> 36:31.689
My back's feeling its age.
Thanks, Luc.

36:32.482 --> 36:33.440
My pleasure, Roger.

36:41.575 --> 36:44.076
Come see me tomorrow, Mr Bouchard.

36:44.744 --> 36:46.662
l'm building a house. No time.

36:47.122 --> 36:50.040
l start at 7:30. You'll be first in line.

36:50.166 --> 36:51.208
l'll bring him.

36:51.334 --> 36:53.002
That's all l need.

36:54.045 --> 36:55.004
7:30.

36:55.547 --> 36:56.505
l'll expect you.

37:01.720 --> 37:03.846
l just love architecture.

37:03.972 --> 37:06.223
l'm crazy about beauty.

37:06.850 --> 37:08.809
At college l was quite the artist.

37:08.935 --> 37:09.727
Wonderful.

37:10.186 --> 37:13.647
l'm on 2 Ministry of Culture committees.

37:13.773 --> 37:14.899
