40:26.508 --> 40:27.674
Well, it happens.

40:28.718 --> 40:31.178
Your wife seems depressed.

40:31.596 --> 40:34.181
l know. l'm getting worried.

40:50.073 --> 40:51.323
Going hunting?

40:53.660 --> 40:55.577
Goose hunting, next week.

40:57.288 --> 40:58.455
With your pal?

40:58.957 --> 40:59.706
Yeah.

41:05.713 --> 41:07.548
