41:08.424 --> 41:09.758
His mom told me.

41:30.864 --> 41:32.030
l better go.

41:33.908 --> 41:34.908
l'll be back.

43:00.620 --> 43:01.703
What's wrong?

43:01.829 --> 43:02.454
Nothing.

43:02.789 --> 43:04.206
l saw you pull in.

43:05.959 --> 43:07.542
What did you do today?

43:09.087 --> 43:09.836
Nothing.

43:10.213 --> 43:10.963
Nothing?

43:11.339 --> 43:12.798
l didn't do any work.

43:15.134 --> 43:16.218
l went to see Roger.

43:18.429 --> 43:19.429
