but was living with Melissa,

45:09.165 --> 45:11.500
and he could go stuff his fantasies.

45:12.251 --> 45:14.211
He moved up north.

45:14.545 --> 45:16.129
Never found anyone else.

45:16.255 --> 45:17.547
He ruined his life.

45:18.800 --> 45:20.842
Trying to be loyal and sincere.

45:57.964 --> 45:59.423
ls it dry enough?

46:00.216 --> 46:02.008
Probably. We'll see.

46:20.361 --> 46:21.945
lt's really smooth.

46:31.497 --> 46:32.581
You're right.

46:33.040 --> 46:33.999
Very mellow.

46:48.639 --> 46:49.514
You OK?

46:50.057 --> 46:51.183
lt's strong.

46:51.309 --> 46:52.642
You could've warned me!

47:25.426 --> 47:26.551
You OK, my love?

47:28.513 --> 47:29.846
l don't feel well.

47:32.475 --> 47:33.892
Want to lie down?

47:36.270 --> 47:37.354
Let me.

47:41.359 --> 47:42.234
l'll take you.

47:44.195 --> 47:45.612
l'll help you up.

47:46.572 --> 47:47.447
Come on.

47:59.710 --> 48:00.752
Are you OK?

48:04.090 --> 48:05.840
l'm fine. lt's over.

48:49.635 --> 48:50.927
There's none left.

48:56.058 --> 48:57.517
She's sick.

48:57.977 --> 48:59.519
Really sick?

49:25.212 --> 49:26.046
So?

49:26.172 --> 49:27.130
Good.

49:27.256 --> 49:27.964
What's my time?

49:32.345 --> 49:33.511
l forgot to click.

49:33.638 --> 49:34.804
Steph, jeez!

49:34.930 --> 49:36.890
Sorry, my mind was elsewhere.

49:37.475 --> 49:38.558
Yeah, but...!

49:38.684 --> 49:39.392
Sorry.

49:42.980 --> 49:44.564
l want to go home.

49:44.690 --> 49:46.024
Get me out of here.

49:46.484 --> 49:48.234
You need treatment.

49:49.028 --> 49:50.987
My brother went through this.

49:51.113 --> 49:52.572
l know what to expect.

49:52.698 --> 49:54.407
Take me home.

49:59.080 --> 50:01.164
l know, l spoke to the nurse.

50:01.290 --> 50:03.041
So, do l bring him home?

50:03.167 --> 50:05.669
We're not equipped here.

50:05.795 --> 50:09.130
He's parked in the fucking hall,
he's miserable.

50:09.256 --> 50:10.465
That's how it is.

50:12.093 --> 50:14.344
