50:14.762 --> 50:15.679
l'll try.

50:16.806 --> 50:18.223
What can l say?

50:18.349 --> 50:20.558
l'm so tired of cases like this.

50:20.685 --> 50:22.143
l understand.

50:40.162 --> 50:41.413
You OK?

51:42.933 --> 51:45.727
We built some beautiful houses.

51:47.438 --> 51:48.938
We tried, anyway.

51:49.982 --> 51:51.399
Not try, dammit!

51:53.235 --> 51:54.402
