56:48.405 --> 56:49.447
On TV.

56:53.243 --> 56:54.452
lt's a documentary.

56:57.039 --> 56:59.373
But reality can't be everywhere.

57:00.542 --> 57:01.375
You know?

57:03.670 --> 57:04.754
Not exactly.

57:09.510 --> 57:11.969
Re... reality can't be everywhere.

57:14.098 --> 57:15.348
There's us and...

57:19.228 --> 57:20.186
Or else...

57:21.105 --> 57:22.271
