57:26.819 --> 57:30.738
l feel panic.

57:32.199 --> 57:32.907
Stop.

58:05.399 --> 58:06.440
Try to sleep.

58:13.532 --> 58:14.657
Come back.

58:15.284 --> 58:16.117
Don't go.

58:17.244 --> 58:18.244
l'll be outside.

58:19.163 --> 58:20.079
No, stay here.

58:22.124 --> 58:23.040
Don't move.

58:27.254 --> 58:28.588
