59:51.713 --> 59:52.505
We're here!

59:54.383 --> 59:57.468
My first contract was an Econoprix drugstore.

59:58.178 --> 59:58.844
The horror!

59:59.429 --> 1:00:02.515
l met the CEO in his 40th-floor office.

1:00:02.641 --> 1:00:05.768
He said, "Our customer lives in an ugly house

1:00:05.894 --> 1:00:07.979
with ugly furniture, ugly curtains,

1:00:08.105 --> 1:00:09.272
on an ugly street.

1:00:09.731 --> 1:00:12.191
l want him to feel right at home.

1:00:12.317 --> 1:00:14.110
l want ugly drugstores.

1:00:14.236 --> 1:00:15.653
lt's made me billions."

1:00:15.988 --> 1:00:18.698
l went to my boss and quit.

1:00:19.283 --> 1:00:20.992
We took over.

1:00:21.118 --> 1:00:23.661
Designed monstrosities that earn millions.

1:00:23.787 --> 1:00:28.124
You're not forced to read a bad book,
or listen to bad music.

1:00:28.750 --> 1:00:30.209
ln elevators.
- Shops.

1:00:30.335 --> 1:00:31.877
Restaurants.

1:00:32.004 --> 1:00:33.170
A building's worse!

1:00:34.047 --> 1:00:38.551
An ugly building that you have to look at
every day poisons your life.

1:00:38.677 --> 1:00:40.344
Most people don't realize.

1:00:40.470 --> 1:00:42.638
Ugliness is a crime against humanity.

1:00:44.099 --> 1:00:44.890
Thanks.

1:00:46.977 --> 1:00:48.561
Your crêpes are exquisite!

1:00:48.687 --> 1:00:49.603
l had help.

1:01:25.349 --> 1:01:26.724
You're too fast for me.

1:01:31.271 --> 1:01:33.147
Your mouth's a popsicle.

1:01:33.732 --> 1:01:34.482
Don't like it?

1:01:34.608 --> 1:01:35.524
On the contrary.

1:01:39.154 --> 1:01:39.904
Let's go.

1:01:47.079 --> 1:01:47.828
Stop!

1:01:49.331 --> 1:01:50.039
What?

1:01:51.333 --> 1:01:52.166
Stop.

1:01:57.005 --> 1:01:57.797
Wait.

1:01:59.758 --> 1:02:00.508
l can't...

1:02:01.134 --> 1:02:02.176
l can't go back up.

1:02:02.302 --> 1:02:03.386
Why not?

1:02:03.512 --> 1:02:04.303
The lift.

1:02:06.014 --> 1:02:07.056
Get the car.

1:02:08.141 --> 1:02:09.100
l'll wait here.

1:02:10.936 --> 1:02:12.561
We've skied here for years.

1:02:13.355 --> 1:02:15.231
You've always taken this lift.

1:02:15.899 --> 1:02:17.024
l can't do it.

1:02:17.567 --> 1:02:18.359
l swear.

1:02:18.485 --> 1:02:19.819
lt's silly. Come on.

1:02:20.695 --> 1:02:21.404
Come with me.

1:02:21.863 --> 1:02:23.739
l'll hold you tight.

1:02:26.284 --> 1:02:27.034
Okay?

1:03:10.120 --> 1:03:11.120
l'm scared.

1:03:12.080 --> 1:03:13.247
We'll fall.

1:03:13.373 --> 1:03:14.206
No, we won't.

1:03:14.666 --> 1:03:15.458
Don't worry.

1:03:15.917 --> 1:03:16.709
We'll be fine.

1:03:18.587 --> 1:03:19.336
Nearly there.

1:03:23.175 --> 1:03:24.300
l can't!

1:03:24.676 --> 1:03:25.801
We're there.

1:03:29.598 --> 1:03:30.431
Let me go!

1:03:30.807 --> 1:03:32.641
Stop!
- Calm down.

1:04:16.102 --> 1:04:17.186
We're going home.

1:04:17.312 --> 1:04:18.646
No need.

1:04:19.022 --> 1:04:21.565
You've only skied one run.

1:04:22.108 --> 1:04:23.484
l'll have a coffee.

1:04:24.152 --> 1:04:24.944
l'll wait.

1:04:26.571 --> 1:04:27.613
You go ski.

1:04:27.739 --> 1:04:29.532
l can't leave you alone.

1:04:29.658 --> 1:04:30.950
lt's OK, don't worry.

1:04:31.409 --> 1:04:33.494
l'll be safe in the restaurant.

1:04:33.954 --> 1:04:34.995
Go have fun.

1:04:35.121 --> 1:04:36.413
No, look at me.

1:04:37.332 --> 1:04:38.165
Are you sure?

1:04:40.126 --> 1:04:41.210
l'm fine.

1:05:16.955 --> 1:05:18.747
What do you want us to do?

1:05:20.709 --> 1:05:22.126
Some sprints?

1:05:24.087 --> 1:05:26.880
Practise passing, maybe?

1:07:55.238 --> 1:07:56.530
lt's funny.

1:07:56.656 --> 1:08:00.242
Have you ever gone on MatchCom

1:08:00.869 --> 1:08:01.702
or eHarmony?

1:08:01.828 --> 1:08:03.078
You visit those sites?

1:08:03.204 --> 1:08:04.663
A girl can dream.

1:08:05.165 --> 1:08:06.874
lt's fascinating.

1:08:07.000 --> 1:08:10.252
People are more and more demanding.

1:08:10.712 --> 1:08:11.670
Thanks.

1:08:11.796 --> 1:08:14.673
The other day a woman was seeking...

1:08:15.008 --> 1:08:17.134
a mycologist, avid cyclist,

1:08:17.260 --> 1:08:19.094
between 35 and 39,

1:08:19.220 --> 1:08:23.015
no beard or moustache, but not bald.

1:08:23.141 --> 1:08:24.600
l mean, really!

1:08:24.726 --> 1:08:25.768
Maybe he exists.

1:08:26.102 --> 1:08:28.353
But that's just the question:

1:08:28.480 --> 1:08:30.647
Today, with the lnternet,

1:08:30.774 --> 1:08:34.109
will everyone find their soulmate?

1:08:34.486 --> 1:08:36.069
With us, it was luck.

1:08:36.863 --> 1:08:39.323
Nicolas and l were neighbors as teens.

1:08:39.449 --> 1:08:40.532
Alas.

1:08:41.826 --> 1:08:42.618
Luck.

1:08:43.077 --> 1:08:45.370
We worked in the same hospital.

1:08:45.497 --> 1:08:46.413
Enfant-Jésus.

1:08:46.539 --> 1:08:47.456
Luck.

1:08:47.957 --> 1:08:49.374
How'd you two meet?

1:08:51.169 --> 1:08:53.962
We were on the varsity tennis team.

1:08:54.464 --> 1:08:55.380
Luck.

1:08:56.966 --> 1:08:59.885
He was a country boy with long legs.

1:09:00.011 --> 1:09:01.345
He'd grown too fast.

1:09:02.680 --> 1:09:04.139
He was timid,

1:09:04.265 --> 1:09:05.390
always blushing.

1:09:06.726 --> 1:09:07.768
So endearing.

1:09:31.376 --> 1:09:32.125
Hi.

1:09:33.837 --> 1:09:34.586
You good?

1:09:40.718 --> 1:09:41.468
Your wife...

1:09:46.266 --> 1:09:47.808
She won't make it alone.

1:09:48.685 --> 1:09:49.852
She won't?

1:09:52.647 --> 1:09:53.981
She needs help.

1:09:55.984 --> 1:09:57.359
l dragged her here.

1:09:59.487 --> 1:10:01.363
Shall l ask around?

1:10:07.328 --> 1:10:08.620
You home tomorrow night?

1:10:09.998 --> 1:10:13.458
No. l have a regional committee meeting.

1:10:14.460 --> 1:10:15.961
ls Melissa going?

1:10:16.671 --> 1:10:19.631
Yeah, she's seeing friends. Why?

1:10:19.757 --> 1:10:21.425
l hoped Steph could visit.

1:10:23.344 --> 1:10:24.553
l'll be in Quebec.

1:10:25.388 --> 1:10:26.221
Sorry.

1:10:29.767 --> 1:10:30.809
l feel guilty.

1:10:33.605 --> 1:10:35.230
l'll see what l can do.

1:10:35.356 --> 1:10:36.690
l'll let you know.

1:10:38.359 --> 1:10:39.109
Thanks.

1:10:39.485 --> 1:10:40.319
Welcome.

1:11:03.968 --> 1:11:05.302
Sure you'll be OK?

1:11:07.430 --> 1:11:08.555
Yeah, yeah.

1:11:11.559 --> 1:11:12.976
You could go stay with Nicolas.

1:11:13.102 --> 1:11:14.978
What for?

1:11:16.522 --> 1:11:18.023
So you're not alone.

1:11:19.734 --> 1:11:20.984
l'm used to it.

1:11:35.541 --> 1:11:36.875
See you tomorrow.

1:12:20.003 --> 1:12:20.961
Goodness!

1:12:26.175 --> 1:12:27.217
Hey, Pascal.

1:12:27.593 --> 1:12:30.387
To what do l owe the unexpected honor?

1:12:30.513 --> 1:12:32.681
You've left your rustic retreat,

1:12:32.807 --> 1:12:34.850
yet snubbed our last opening.

1:12:34.976 --> 1:12:36.435
l work non-stop.

1:12:37.687 --> 1:12:38.603
Hello, madame.

1:12:42.108 --> 1:12:42.941
You've met?

1:12:44.736 --> 1:12:47.070
Yes, l have a project for them.

1:12:48.448 --> 1:12:50.741
A project in Toronto?

1:12:50.867 --> 1:12:52.534
We're still just talking.

1:12:54.328 --> 1:12:55.495
l want to hear.

1:12:55.621 --> 1:12:56.371
Of course.

1:12:57.165 --> 1:12:59.750
Can l offer you two a drink?

1:13:01.335 --> 1:13:03.920
We have a meeting with a banker

1:13:04.756 --> 1:13:06.173
about the project.

1:13:08.134 --> 1:13:09.217
ln Quebec City?

1:13:09.677 --> 1:13:11.970
Yeah, complicated financing.

1:13:15.892 --> 1:13:17.684
Have a good meeting.

1:13:17.810 --> 1:13:18.477
Thank you.

1:13:25.818 --> 1:13:28.862
Come back to Quebec without telling me,

1:13:30.323 --> 1:13:31.740
l'll be quite angry.

1:13:32.784 --> 1:13:35.035
l'll let you know. l swear.

1:13:35.495 --> 1:13:36.453
See you!

1:17:14.380 --> 1:17:15.630
How are you?

1:17:15.756 --> 1:17:16.464
Fine, you?

1:17:16.590 --> 1:17:17.716
Just great.

1:17:17.842 --> 1:17:19.467
We got the Hydro contract.

1:17:19.844 --> 1:17:20.552
Fantastic.

1:17:21.971 --> 1:17:23.054
ls Stéphanie here?

1:17:23.681 --> 1:17:25.432
No, she had to work.

1:17:25.933 --> 1:17:27.642
Tell her l said hi.

1:17:28.269 --> 1:17:28.977
Will do.

1:25:13.817 --> 1:25:14.525
Steph!

1:25:17.196 --> 1:25:18.237
What?

1:25:23.911 --> 1:25:24.869
You scared me.

1:25:33.504 --> 1:25:34.962
Why are the rifles out?

1:25:42.763 --> 1:25:44.138
You haven't moved?

1:25:47.976 --> 1:25:49.393
Did you eat?

1:25:54.358 --> 1:25:55.399
This is crazy.

1:25:56.318 --> 1:25:57.902
Not hungry.

1:27:12.936 --> 1:27:14.270
How are you today?

1:27:21.445 --> 1:27:22.445
You know what?

1:27:24.239 --> 1:27:26.198
l've had an amazing offer.

1:27:27.868 --> 1:27:29.118
The Cistercians.

1:27:30.996 --> 1:27:32.705
To build an abbey.

1:27:35.709 --> 1:27:36.542
Just imagine.

1:27:38.629 --> 1:27:39.754
Like John Pawson!

1:27:43.216 --> 1:27:45.134
l took you to his monastery

1:27:45.844 --> 1:27:47.178
in Bohemia.

1:27:51.099 --> 1:27:51.807
Remember?

1:27:58.148 --> 1:28:00.232
lt's the opportunity of a lifetime.

1:28:02.694 --> 1:28:03.736
lsn't that great?

1:28:31.556 --> 1:28:32.890
l have to leave.

1:28:33.433 --> 1:28:34.308
l have to work.

1:28:35.852 --> 1:28:37.561
Hockey, hunting...

1:28:38.522 --> 1:28:39.480
lt's not enough.

1:28:42.359 --> 1:28:44.485
Even love's not enough.

1:28:46.989 --> 1:28:47.989
lt is for me.

1:28:52.494 --> 1:28:54.120
Everybody's different.

1:28:59.126 --> 1:29:00.710
l'll sell this place.

1:29:30.824 --> 1:29:32.450
She's by the river today.

1:29:32.576 --> 1:29:33.409
Thanks.

1:30:05.358 --> 1:30:06.984
lt's so hard to explain.

1:30:08.487 --> 1:30:10.321
Even to imagine.

1:30:11.448 --> 1:30:12.865
lt's so painful.

1:30:15.077 --> 1:30:17.036
l wanted to rip my head off...

1:30:23.168 --> 1:30:25.503
to kill myself, just to stop it.

1:30:25.629 --> 1:30:27.254
To stop the pain.

1:30:34.930 --> 1:30:37.264
l thought l was attracted to Melissa.

1:30:39.726 --> 1:30:40.643
l know.

1:30:42.312 --> 1:30:43.479
How did you know?

1:30:43.897 --> 1:30:45.981
l saw you kissing one day.

1:30:46.650 --> 1:30:47.775
At the golf club.

1:30:52.322 --> 1:30:53.572
And you said nothing?

1:30:53.698 --> 1:30:54.865
What could l say?

1:30:55.367 --> 1:30:56.450
l dunno.

1:30:57.369 --> 1:30:59.078
You could've slapped me.

1:30:59.538 --> 1:31:01.163
Or called me a slut.

1:31:03.125 --> 1:31:04.333
Not my style.

1:31:04.668 --> 1:31:05.459
Alas.

1:31:05.794 --> 1:31:06.460
Sorry.

1:31:18.431 --> 1:31:21.350
l had a fling with a girl from Toronto.

1:31:23.812 --> 1:31:24.687
You did?

1:31:26.314 --> 1:31:27.982
She even came to Quebec City.

1:31:31.027 --> 1:31:32.444
How long did it last?

1:31:33.822 --> 1:31:34.572
2 nights.

1:32:04.644 --> 1:32:05.978
SOLD

1:32:11.985 --> 1:32:13.444
What's your title?

1:32:14.070 --> 1:32:16.947
3rd assistant coach of the national team.

1:32:19.201 --> 1:32:20.201
lmpressive.

1:32:21.036 --> 1:32:21.911
Yeah, right.

1:32:29.294 --> 1:32:30.336
And your abbey?

1:32:30.837 --> 1:32:31.503
Coming along.

1:32:43.808 --> 1:32:45.643
Say you'll always love me.

1:32:52.484 --> 1:32:53.359
Always.

1:33:26.726 --> 1:33:28.477
Amazing radishes.

1:33:29.896 --> 1:33:31.647
The first of the season.

1:34:16.443 --> 1:34:18.652
At the Canadian delegation.

1:34:21.740 --> 1:34:23.449
Again, congratulations.

1:34:23.825 --> 1:34:24.575
Thanks.

1:34:26.536 --> 1:34:27.453
Thanks a lot.

1:34:38.089 --> 1:34:39.214
Who was that?

1:34:39.883 --> 1:34:40.924
A lady...

1:34:42.052 --> 1:34:43.177
from my past.

1:34:44.387 --> 1:34:46.722
You have many ladies in your past.

1:34:47.932 --> 1:34:49.516
No, not really.

1:34:51.144 --> 1:34:53.020
Should l believe you?

1:34:53.396 --> 1:34:55.189
Always, darling.

1:34:56.024 --> 1:34:57.191
Are you hungry?

1:34:57.317 --> 1:34:58.525
Famished.

1:34:59.194 --> 1:35:00.027
Wait here.

1:35:18.505 --> 1:35:19.380
lt's me.

1:35:19.839 --> 1:35:21.256
Ready for your medal?

1:35:21.383 --> 1:35:22.549
l have it already.

1:35:22.675 --> 1:35:24.551
l thought it was tomorrow.

1:35:24.677 --> 1:35:25.761
No, today.

1:35:25.887 --> 1:35:27.221
Fantastic.

1:35:28.556 --> 1:35:31.517
You know the place Simon and l bought?

1:35:31.643 --> 1:35:34.937
There's a leak in the ceiling.

1:35:35.063 --> 1:35:36.563
l'm in Paris.

1:35:36.689 --> 1:35:40.067
l know that. When you come back.

1:35:40.193 --> 1:35:42.486
Then we see Juana's family in Madrid.

1:35:43.196 --> 1:35:44.405
When you're back.

1:35:44.823 --> 1:35:46.615
OK, l'll try to drop by.

1:35:46.950 --> 1:35:48.117
That's sweet.

1:35:49.452 --> 1:35:50.536
l love you.

1:35:51.996 --> 1:35:52.788
Me too.

1:35:54.791 --> 1:35:55.791
See you soon.

1:36:01.423 --> 1:36:02.673
Salami.

1:36:03.216 --> 1:36:04.258
Maravilloso!

1:41:49.437 --> 1:41:52.481
Subtitles: Robert Gray, Kinograph
